description: The Amazon is looking for her first win this season. She hasn't even scored a style point yet, and has lost by an average of 207 points per match. The Grappler is new to US; however, her husband was a talented wrestler in [REDACTED] and has been showing her the basics. As always experience wins out. The Grappler gets her first taste of getting fucked hard on the mat in RD4.
title: The Amazon (2-5)
